Phase 1 — Character System & Mode Entry (Launch)
Dashboard Entry Point

Replace Upload Workout button with Enter Adventure Mode
Move Upload Workout to Profile menu or secondary action

First-Time Onboarding

Tapping "Enter Adventure Mode" triggers character selection
No proactive prompt — discoverable, easter egg feel
Clear exit path back to Default Mode at any time

Character Selection Screen

Browsable grid or carousel of all 24 characters
Selection: Archetype → Gender → Color
Brief intro narrative line on confirm
Character stored in user profile (persists across sessions)

Character Editing

Accessible from Adventure Mode settings or Profile
Swap freely — never resets long-term progression
Progression reset is a separate protected flow

Adventure Mode Shell

Adventure-themed UI applied when mode is active
Strava sync continues as normal underneath

Phase 1 Deliverables

 24 character illustrations (Canva AI)
 Dashboard CTA button swap
 Character selection screen
 Character persistence (profile data model update)
 Adventure Mode themed shell/layout
 Mode toggle (enter/exit) with state management
 Character swap settings flow


